                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6444" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-1640</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8104 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">设施花卉路在何方？行业领跑者爱必达的坚守与蜕变</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Where Should Facilities Flower Go? The Perseverance and Transformation of Industry Leader Aibida</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">张立明，杨玥（通讯作者），卢启程，薛允，赵漫，房彦兵</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云南财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">周勇</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云南爱必达园艺科技有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农林牧副渔业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">17 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">设施花卉；战略目标；核心能力</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Facilities flowers; Strategic objectives; Core competence</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2017年前后，面对“由蓝转红”的市场环境和日趋严重的资金压力，云南爱必达园艺科技有限公司（简称“爱必达”）及时调整战略目标，成功从花卉种植商转型为综合服务提供商。经过连续四年的快速增长，爱必达已成为国内设施花卉行业的领跑者。那么爱必达是如何实现成功转型的呢？本案例将以战略目标调整为切入点，回顾爱必达自创立以来的发展历程，着重描述爱必达立足自身实际，紧抓外部机遇，凭借集成创新提升综合服务能力，最终成功从设施花卉种植商转型为综合服务提供商的全过程。本案例旨在帮助学生更好地运用战略管理的相关理论和分析工具，深入理解企业战略目标调整的决策逻辑和实施路径，掌握通过提升战略执行力来实现战略目标的有效举措，并为相关领域企业转型升级提供模式、机制和路径等方面的启示和借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In 2017, facing the market environment of &quot;turning from blue to red&quot; and the increasingly serious financial pressure, Yunnan Aibida Horticultural Technology Co., Ltd. (hereinafter referred to as &quot;Aibida&quot;) timely adjusted its strategy objectives and successfully transformed from a flower grower to a comprehensive service provider. After four consecutive years of rapid growth, Aibida has become a leader in the domestic facility flower industry. How does Aibida achieve successful transformation? This case will take the adjustment of strategic objectives as the starting point, review the development process of Aibida since its establishment, and focus on describing the whole process of Aibida&#39;s successful transformation from a facility flower grower to a comprehensive service provider, Base on its own reality, Aibida grasped external opportunities and improved its comprehensive service capability with integrated innovation. This case aims to help students make better use of relevant theories and analysis tools of strategic management, deeply understand the decision-making logic and implementation path of enterprise strategic goal adjustment, master effective measures to achieve strategic goals by improving strategic execution, and provide enlightenment and reference in terms of mode, mechanism and path for enterprise transformation and upgrading in relevant fields.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业生命周期；战略目标的概念；SMART原则；PESTEL分析；五力模型；内部要素分析；核心能力的概念；VIRO模型；战略执行力的概念；提升战略执行力的三个活动</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-08</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
